<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.1">
<l>ūrellān tuñci yulakellā naḷḷiruḷāy</l>
<l>nīrellān tēṟiyōr nīḷiravāy nīṇṭatāl</l>
<l>pārellā muṇṭanam pāmpaṇaiyāṉ vārāṉā</l>
<l>lārellē valviṉaiyē ṉāvikāp pāriṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While all the village sleeps, while all the world there is dense darkness,</l>
<l>while all the waters are clear, as one long night [time] grows long.</l>
<l>Our man on the snake bed who ate all the earth will not come.</l>
<l>Who, friend, will guard the soul of me with harsh Karma this much?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
